# Cloudflare Workers static assets honors this file. The default content-type
# for `.md` doesn't carry `charset=utf-8`, so en-dashes / curly quotes / other
# non-ASCII bytes can decode as Windows-1252 mojibake (e2 80 93 → "â€"") in
# clients that don't assume UTF-8. Set the charset explicitly here.
#
# `Content-Disposition: inline` keeps the file viewed in-browser, while the
# `filename` argument gives "Save as" a recognizable name (and is picked up
# by some browsers as the tab title for non-HTML content).
#
# Fork knob: change the filenames below to match `siteConfig.name` in
# `lib/site.ts` if you fork this repo.
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/headers/

/resume.md
  Content-Type: text/markdown; charset=utf-8
  Content-Disposition: inline; filename="Nathan Cheng - Resume.md"

/:variant/resume.md
  Content-Type: text/markdown; charset=utf-8
  Content-Disposition: inline; filename="Nathan Cheng - Resume.md"

/resume.json
  Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
  Content-Disposition: inline; filename="Nathan Cheng - Resume.json"

/:variant/resume.json
  Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
  Content-Disposition: inline; filename="Nathan Cheng - Resume.json"
